%N A395629 Infinite square array where the n-th row gives the continued fraction of Product_{k=1..n} (sqrt(k+1)-sqrt(k)); listed by falling antidiagonals.
%F A395629 row(n+1) = row(n)*(sqrt(n+1) - sqrt(n)), with row(1) = sqrt(2)-1.
%F A395629 T(n+1, 1) ~ T(n, 1)*(sqrt(n) + sqrt(n+1)).
%e A395629   n | C(n) = Product_{k=1..n} sqrt(k+1)-sqrt(k)
